---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Plan a Visit
description: "Everything you need to know before your first visit to Summitville Wesleyan Bible Church."
---

<!-- ── PAGE HERO ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Plan Your Visit</h1>
    <p>We can't wait to meet you. Here's everything you need to know.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── SERVICE TIMES + ADDRESS ──────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="visit-cols">

      <!-- Left: info blocks -->
      <div>
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>Service Times</h3>
          {% for st in site.serviceTimes %}
          <p>
            <strong>{{ st.name }}:</strong> {{ st.time }}
            {% if st.location %}<br><span style="color:var(--text-muted); font-size:.88rem;">{{ st.location }}</span>{% endif %}
          </p>
          {% endfor %}
          <p class="mt-2" style="font-size:.88rem; color:var(--text-muted);">
            ✏️ <em>Update times in <code>src/_data/site.js</code></em>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>Location</h3>
          <p>{{ site.address.full }}</p>
          <a href="{{ site.address.mapsUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-navy mt-2">
            Get Directions
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>What to Expect</h3>
          <div class="expect-grid">
            <div class="expect-item">
              <span class="expect-icon">🅿️</span>
              <p><strong>Parking</strong> — Free parking is available on site. Accessible spaces are located near the main entrance.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="expect-item">
              <span class="expect-icon">👕</span>
              <p><strong>Attire</strong> — Come as you are! You'll see people in everything from jeans to dress clothes. There's no dress code here.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="expect-item">
              <span class="expect-icon">👶</span>
              <p><strong>Children</strong> — We have age-appropriate programming for children during the service. Kids check-in begins 15 minutes before the service.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="expect-item">
              <span class="expect-icon">⏱️</span>
              <p><strong>Service Length</strong> — Our Sunday morning service runs approximately 60–75 minutes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="expect-item">
              <span class="expect-icon">🎶</span>
              <p><strong>Worship Style</strong> — We blend contemporary worship music with classic hymns in a warm, participatory atmosphere.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="expect-item">
              <span class="expect-icon">☕</span>
              <p><strong>After the Service</strong> — Stick around! We have a time of fellowship after each service. Coffee and conversation welcome.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: map + first-timer tips -->
      <div>
        <div class="map-frame mb-4">
          <!--
            To add a Google Map embed:
            1. Go to maps.google.com and search for your church address.
            2. Click Share → Embed a map → Copy the <iframe> code.
            3. Replace the placeholder below with that iframe code.
          -->
          <div class="map-placeholder">
            <span class="map-pin">📍</span>
            <p>{{ site.address.full }}</p>
            <p style="margin-top:.5rem;">
              <a href="{{ site.address.mapsUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-navy mt-2">
                Open in Google Maps
              </a>
            </p>
            <p style="font-size:.8rem; margin-top:1rem; color:var(--text-muted);">
              ✏️ Replace this placeholder with a Google Maps embed in <code>src/visit.njk</code>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>New Here? Here's a Tip</h3>
          <p>
            When you walk in the door, look for someone wearing a <strong>Welcome
            Team</strong> badge — they are here to answer any questions and help
            you find your way around. Don't hesitate to say hello!
          </p>
          <p>
            After the service, we'd love to get you a <strong>Welcome Gift</strong>
            — stop by the Welcome Table in the foyer to pick yours up and learn
            more about getting connected.
          </p>
          <a href="/connect/" class="btn btn-outline-navy mt-2">Contact Us with Questions</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── SERVICE TIMES BAND ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="service-band">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>When We Meet</h2>
      <p>All are welcome. No reservation needed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="times-grid">
      {% for st in site.serviceTimes %}
      <div class="time-card">
        <h3>{{ st.name }}</h3>
        <div class="time-value">{{ st.time }}</div>
        <div class="time-sub">{{ st.location }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
